Dialogue: 11,0:22:12.85,0:22:17.85,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}Vibration, an undelivered emotion
Dialogue: 11,0:22:24.73,0:22:30.57,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}This place exists as a sequence of layers
