Dialogue: 11,0:22:59.60,0:23:02.94,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}In which I can be found right here
Dialogue: 11,0:23:03.82,0:23:07.24,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}I'll tell you my feelings that I keep inside
Dialogue: 11,0:23:07.24,0:23:10.36,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}I remain in solitude, while in hold of
Dialogue: 11,0:23:10.36,0:23:16.12,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}A countless number of infinitely expansive universes
Dialogue: 11,0:23:16.12,0:23:19.54,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}That's why I'll make sure
Dialogue: 11,0:23:19.54,0:23:22.63,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}For the sake of your tomorrow
Dialogue: 11,0:23:22.63,0:23:28.42,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}That the blasphemy of the God ruling this universe
Dialogue: 11,0:23:28.80,0:23:31.89,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}Will never be repeated
